explanation: Compute prefix and suffix OR arrays to isolate the effect of doubling any single element k times. For each index, the OR of the rest is prefix[i] | suffix[i+1]; OR-ing with nums[i] << k gives the maximum possible OR when all k operations are applied to that element.

